rses-al-laan","tag-manners-adab","tag-travel-al-safr"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-8mW","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":14681,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/09\/not-cursing-animals\/","url_meta":{"origin":32174,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Cursing: Do not curse animals and objects","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Barzah al-Aslami reported: A young woman was riding a camel upon which were people\u2019s luggage. When she saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and the pass of the mountain became narrow, the woman said to the camel, \u201cGo ahead!\u201d When it did not move, she said,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32176,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/be-careful-what-you-curse-for\/","url_meta":{"origin":32174,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Cursing: Be careful what you curse for","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was riding on a journey and a man cursed his she-camel. The Prophet said, \u201cWhere is the owner of the she-camel?\u201d The man said, \u201cIt is me.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cLeave her behind, for your curse has been answered.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41419,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/10\/06\/prohibition-branding-face\/","url_meta":{"origin":32174,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Cruelty: Prohibition of branding and striking the face","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 6, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, passed by an animal who had been branded on the face and its nostrils were smoking. The Prophet said, \u201cAllah has cursed whoever has done this. Do not brand anyone on the face, nor strike it.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14677,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/06\/09\/haram-to-curse-animals\/","url_meta":{"origin":32174,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Cursing: Forbidden to curse animals","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 9, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Imran ibn Husayn reported: We were with the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, during one of his journeys while a woman from the Ansar was on a camel. She disparaged it and cursed it. When the Prophet heard it, he said, \u201cUnload the camel and set\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15468,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/fear-allah-animals-ride\/","url_meta":{"origin":32174,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Animals: Fear Allah in creatures you own","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Ja\u2019far reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, entered a garden among the Ansar. When a camel saw the Prophet, it\u00a0started weeping and making sounds as its tears flowed. The Prophet came to it and patted it on the head, so it became silent.\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41235,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/27\/dua-for-the-ill\/","url_meta":{"origin":32174,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Dua: The Prophet calls upon Allah for the ill","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 27, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would say when he visited the sick, \u201cTake away the pain, O Lord of the people, and heal it, for You are the Healer. There is no healing but Your healing, a healing that leaves no trace of illness.\u201d Source:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32174","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,